{"number":77,"ayahs":[{"numberInSurah":1,"arabic":" وَٱلْمُرْسَلَـٰتِ عُرْفًا","translation":"By those [winds] sent forth in gusts","transliteration":"Walmursalati AAurfa","page":580},{"numberInSurah":2,"arabic":"فَٱلْعَـٰصِفَـٰتِ عَصْفًا","translation":"And the winds that blow violently","transliteration":"FalAAasifati AAasfa","page":580},{"numberInSurah":3,"arabic":"وَٱلنَّـٰشِرَٰتِ نَشْرًا","translation":"And [by] the winds that spread [clouds]","transliteration":"Wannashirati nashra","page":580},{"numberInSurah":4,"arabic":"فَٱلْفَـٰرِقَـٰتِ فَرْقًا","translation":"And those [angels] who bring criterion","transliteration":"Falfariqati farqa","page":580},{"numberInSurah":5,"arabic":"فَٱلْمُلْقِيَـٰتِ ذِكْرًا","translation":"And those [angels] who deliver a message.","transliteration":"Falmulqiyati thikra","page":580},{"numberInSurah":6,"arabic":"عُذْرًا أَوْ نُذْرًا","translation":"As justification or warning,","transliteration":"AAuthran aw nuthra","page":580},{"numberInSurah":7,"arabic":"إِنَّمَا تُوعَدُونَ لَوَٰقِعٌ","translation":"Indeed, what you are promised is to occur.","transliteration":"Innama tooAAadoona lawaqiAA","page":580},{"numberInSurah":8,"arabic":"فَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ طُمِسَتْ","translation":"So when the stars are obliterated","transliteration":"Fa-itha annujoomu tumisat","page":580},{"numberInSurah":9,"arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ فُرِجَتْ","translation":"And when the heaven is opened","transliteration":"Wa-itha assamao furijat","page":580},{"numberInSurah":10,"arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلْجِبَالُ نُسِفَتْ","translation":"And when the mountains are blown away","transliteration":"Wa-itha aljibalu nusifat","page":580},{"numberInSurah":11,"arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلرُّسُلُ أُقِّتَتْ","translation":"And when the messengers' time has come...","transliteration":"Wa-itha arrusulu oqqitat","page":580},{"numberInSurah":12,"arabic":"لِأَىِّ يَوْمٍ أُجِّلَتْ","translation":"For what Day was it postponed?","transliteration":"Li-ayyi yawmin ojjilat","page":580},{"numberInSurah":13,"arabic":"لِيَوْمِ ٱلْفَصْلِ","translation":"For the Day of Judgement.","transliteration":"Liyawmi alfasl","page":580},{"numberInSurah":14,"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا يَوْمُ ٱلْفَصْلِ","translation":"And what can make you know what is the Day of Judgement?","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma yawmualfasl","page":580},{"numberInSurah":15,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":580},{"numberInSurah":16,"arabic":"أَلَمْ نُهْلِكِ ٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","translation":"Did We not destroy the former peoples?","transliteration":"Alam nuhliki al-awwaleen","page":580},{"numberInSurah":17,"arabic":"ثُمَّ نُتْبِعُهُمُ ٱلْـَٔاخِرِينَ","translation":"Then We will follow them with the later ones.","transliteration":"Thumma nutbiAAuhumu al-akhireen","page":580},{"numberInSurah":18,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ نَفْعَلُ بِٱلْمُجْرِمِينَ","translation":"Thus do We deal with the criminals.","transliteration":"Kathalika nafAAalu bilmujrimeen","page":580},{"numberInSurah":19,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":580},{"numberInSurah":20,"arabic":"أَلَمْ نَخْلُقكُّم مِّن مَّآءٍ مَّهِينٍ","translation":"Did We not create you from a liquid disdained?","transliteration":"Alam nakhluqkum min ma-in maheen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":21,"arabic":"فَجَعَلْنَـٰهُ فِى قَرَارٍ مَّكِينٍ","translation":"And We placed it in a firm lodging [i.e., the womb]","transliteration":"FajaAAalnahu fee qararinmakeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":22,"arabic":"إِلَىٰ قَدَرٍ مَّعْلُومٍ","translation":"For a known extent.","transliteration":"Ila qadarin maAAloom","page":581},{"numberInSurah":23,"arabic":"فَقَدَرْنَا فَنِعْمَ ٱلْقَـٰدِرُونَ","translation":"And We determined [it], and excellent [are We] to determine.","transliteration":"Faqadarna faniAAma alqadiroon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":24,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":25,"arabic":"أَلَمْ نَجْعَلِ ٱلْأَرْضَ كِفَاتًا","translation":"Have We not made the earth a container","transliteration":"Alam najAAali al-arda kifata","page":581},{"numberInSurah":26,"arabic":"أَحْيَآءً وَأَمْوَٰتًا","translation":"Of the living and the dead?","transliteration":"Ahyaan waamwata","page":581},{"numberInSurah":27,"arabic":"وَجَعَلْنَا فِيهَا رَوَٰسِىَ شَـٰمِخَـٰتٍ وَأَسْقَيْنَـٰكُم مَّآءً فُرَاتًا","translation":"And We placed therein lofty, firmly set mountains and have given you to drink sweet water.","transliteration":"WajaAAalna feeha rawasiyashamikhatin waasqaynakum maan furata","page":581},{"numberInSurah":28,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":29,"arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰ مَا كُنتُم بِهِۦ تُكَذِّبُونَ","translation":"[They will be told], \"Proceed to that which you used to deny.","transliteration":"Intaliqoo ila ma kuntumbihi tukaththiboon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":30,"arabic":"ٱنطَلِقُوٓا۟ إِلَىٰ ظِلٍّ ذِى ثَلَـٰثِ شُعَبٍ","translation":"Proceed to a shadow [of smoke] having three columns.","transliteration":"Intaliqoo ila thillinthee thalathi shuAAab","page":581},{"numberInSurah":31,"arabic":"لَّا ظَلِيلٍ وَلَا يُغْنِى مِنَ ٱللَّهَبِ","translation":"[But having] no cool shade and availing not against the flame.\"","transliteration":"La thaleelin walayughnee mina allahab","page":581},{"numberInSurah":32,"arabic":"إِنَّهَا تَرْمِى بِشَرَرٍ كَٱلْقَصْرِ","translation":"Indeed, it throws sparks [as huge] as a fortress,","transliteration":"Innaha tarmee bishararin kalqasr","page":581},{"numberInSurah":33,"arabic":"كَأَنَّهُۥ جِمَـٰلَتٌ صُفْرٌ","translation":"As if they were yellowish [black] camels.","transliteration":"Kaannahu jimalatun sufr","page":581},{"numberInSurah":34,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":35,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا يَوْمُ لَا يَنطِقُونَ","translation":"This is a Day they will not speak,","transliteration":"Hatha yawmu la yantiqoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":36,"arabic":"وَلَا يُؤْذَنُ لَهُمْ فَيَعْتَذِرُونَ","translation":"Nor will it be permitted for them to make an excuse.","transliteration":"Wala yu/thanu lahum fayaAAtathiroon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":37,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":38,"arabic":"هَـٰذَا يَوْمُ ٱلْفَصْلِ ۖ جَمَعْنَـٰكُمْ وَٱلْأَوَّلِينَ","translation":"This is the Day of Judgement; We will have assembled you and the former peoples.","transliteration":"Hatha yawmu alfasli jamaAAnakumwal-awwaleen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":39,"arabic":"فَإِن كَانَ لَكُمْ كَيْدٌ فَكِيدُونِ","translation":"So if you have a plan, then plan against Me.","transliteration":"Fa-in kana lakum kaydun fakeedoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":40,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":41,"arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلْمُتَّقِينَ فِى ظِلَـٰلٍ وَعُيُونٍ","translation":"Indeed, the righteous will be among shades and springs","transliteration":"Inna almuttaqeena fee thilalinwaAAuyoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":42,"arabic":"وَفَوَٰكِهَ مِمَّا يَشْتَهُونَ","translation":"And fruits from whatever they desire,","transliteration":"Wafawakiha mimma yashtahoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":43,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟ وَٱشْرَبُوا۟ هَنِيٓـًٔۢا بِمَا كُنتُمْ تَعْمَلُونَ","translation":"[Being told], \"Eat and drink in satisfaction for what you used to do.\"","transliteration":"Kuloo washraboo hanee-an bimakuntum taAAmaloon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":44,"arabic":"إِنَّا كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلْمُحْسِنِينَ","translation":"Indeed, We thus reward the doers of good.","transliteration":"Inna kathalika najzee almuhsineen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":45,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":46,"arabic":"كُلُوا۟ وَتَمَتَّعُوا۟ قَلِيلًا إِنَّكُم مُّجْرِمُونَ","translation":"[O disbelievers], eat and enjoy yourselves a little; indeed, you are criminals.","transliteration":"Kuloo watamattaAAoo qaleelan innakummujrimoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":47,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":48,"arabic":"وَإِذَا قِيلَ لَهُمُ ٱرْكَعُوا۟ لَا يَرْكَعُونَ","translation":"And when it is said to them, \"Bow [in prayer],\" they do not bow.","transliteration":"Wa-itha qeela lahumu irkaAAoo layarkaAAoon","page":581},{"numberInSurah":49,"arabic":"وَيْلٌ يَوْمَئِذٍ لِّلْمُكَذِّبِينَ","translation":"Woe, that Day, to the deniers.","transliteration":"Waylun yawma-ithin lilmukaththibeen","page":581},{"numberInSurah":50,"arabic":"فَبِأَىِّ حَدِيثٍۭ بَعْدَهُۥ يُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"Then in what statement after it [i.e., the Qur’ān] will they believe?","transliteration":"Fabi-ayyi hadeethin baAAdahuyu/minoon","page":581}]}